data.description: Highly desirable Bay Highlands community.  Spacious home over 3,000 sq ft.   Incredible fenced yard with fire pit area and also plenty of room for a pool.  4 Large bedrooms.  Finished lower level with walkout to this amazing yard.   Screened porch perfect for relaxing or entertaining.   Oversized garage,   Newer roof and siding and windows are also in great shape!  Great home to make your own and priced accordingly.    Community has a website for information and bylaws as well.   www.bayhighlands.org
